%H A132623 Paul D. Hanna, <a href="/A132623/b132623.txt">Rows n = 0..45, flattened.</a>
%F A132623 G.f. of column k: (k+1)*x^(k+1) = Sum_{n>=0} T(n,k) * x^n * (1-x)^(n-k) / Product_{j=k+1..n-1} (1+j*x).
%F A132623 T(n,k) = [x^n] { (k+1)*x^(k+1) - Sum_{m=k+1..n-1} T(m,k)*x^m*(1-x)^(m-k) / Product_{j=k+1..m-1} (1+j*x) } for n>k with T(n,k)=0 when k>=n.
